1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
12 minutes of morning light
changed my entire day.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:06,000
I used to wake up, grab my phone, and stay
inside until noon. By 2 PM I was useless.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:16,000
Morning light tells your brain to start the wake-up process.
Without it, you're running on a dimmed clock all day.

4
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:24,000
Within 60 minutes of waking: go outside. Even cloudy light
is 10x brighter than indoor. 12 minutes is enough.

5
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:30,000
VOLT Sleep gives you 1 action
per day. Free. Link in bio.

